.TH LOA-PRACTICE 1 "2026-03-23" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
practice \- Set practice status for a sheet music entry
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> practice
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prompts for an item reference and a practice status.
.br
Only applies to \fBSheetMusic\fR entries.
.br
Supported statuses:
.br
\fBUnstarted\fR, \fBLearning\fR, \fBRehearsing\fR, \fBPerformance-ready\fR, \fBMastered\fR.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> practice
.br
Sheet music reference: b0042
.br
Practice status: Rehearsing
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-details(1), loa-sheet-stats(1), loa-list-sheet(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Generated for the Library Of Alexandria project.
